{"tid":1970083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國的死亡病例突破1萬　官員形容是陰暗的一日","createTime":"2020-04-13T01:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T02:07:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5abc88833179fe9cc4e90d21a187f977f265daef","tid":1970083,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T01:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1520302_1_L_20200413021247.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1520302_1_L_20200413021247.jpg&h=408e90a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國單日新增737宗新型肺炎死亡病例，成為美國、西班牙、意大利及法國後，第五個突破1萬人死亡的國家。<br />\n<br />\n衛生大臣夏國賢形容，死亡人數突破1萬是陰暗的一日，顯示病毒的嚴重性，亦反映民眾留在家中顯得重要，呼籲民眾繼續遵守社交距離措施。<br />\n<br />\n當局說，倫敦的住院人數正穩定下來，但在西北、約克郡及東北地區有上升趨勢。有政府科學專家小組成員認為，英國可能是歐洲受疫情最嚴重影響的國家之一，相比之下德國的檢測規模之大，令住院人數維持低水平，認為英國可以汲取經驗。"},{"pid":"8d727184ab87b9410b960c89dc8056929b214f2b","tid":1970083,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T01:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續捐錢俾cho 啦"},{"pid":"c7cab87ee7bce682f2b6bee6946092e493903229","tid":1970083,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T01:34:13.000Z","msg":"奶共狗，有排你陰暗丫仆街"},{"pid":"176ff25994e7838b97cbc0b13670746f1faf8aa2","tid":1970083,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T01:43:30.000Z","msg":"侵侵<br />\n@realDonaldTrump<br />\n轉推福克斯節目，包含以下幾方面內容：<br />\n<br />\n1. 把製造業從中共國遷回美國，<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">與中共脫鈎</span></span></span><br />\n2. 中共撒謊，民眾喪命<br />\n3. 不是中國人民的錯，都是中共政府作的惡<br />\n4. 中共是美國最大的威脅，是無可比擬的<br />\n5. 美國人民覺醒了<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1249487975651528704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1249487975651528704&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWZS3ibw